&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Community engagement is at the heart of OONI’s work, as &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/data/"&gt;OONI data&lt;/a&gt; on internet censorship depends on people running &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/install/"&gt;OONI Probe&lt;/a&gt; around the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interested in engaging your communities with OONI censorship measurement?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The OONI Outreach Kit includes &lt;strong&gt;materials that you are encouraged to use&lt;/strong&gt; as part of your OONI community engagement efforts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The OONI Outreach Kit is translated into &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/ru/support/ooni-outreach-kit/"&gt;Russian&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/fr/support/ooni-outreach-kit/"&gt;French&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/es/support/ooni-outreach-kit/"&gt;Spanish&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/sw/support/ooni-outreach-kit/"&gt;Swahili&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/ar/support/ooni-outreach-kit/"&gt;Arabic&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/fa/support/ooni-outreach-kit/"&gt;Farsi&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
