&lt;p&gt;We provide 2 OONI brochures that include information about using OONI tools and data for investigating internet censorship around the world.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>User Guide: OONI Explorer</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-explorer/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-explorer/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Last updated:&lt;/strong&gt; 15th March 2023&lt;/p&gt;











&lt;div&gt;
 &lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-explorer/images/image67.png"&gt;
 &lt;img
 src="https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-explorer/images/image67_hu_fdea6fac15c47ec5.png"

 
 
 title="OONI Explorer"
 
 alt="OONI Explorer"
 
 /&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/"&gt;OONI Explorer&lt;/a&gt; is an open data resource on internet censorship around the world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This user guide provides &lt;strong&gt;step-by-step instructions&lt;/strong&gt; on how to use OONI Explorer to investigate internet censorship worldwide.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will get from this guide:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Learn how to use &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://explorer.ooni.org/"&gt;OONI Explorer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Discover &lt;strong&gt;blocked websites and apps&lt;/strong&gt; around the world&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Access &lt;strong&gt;measurement data&lt;/strong&gt; that can serve as evidence of internet censorship&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>User Guide: OONI Probe Command Line Interface (CLI)</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-probe-cli/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-probe-cli/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Last updated:&lt;/strong&gt; 29th August 2022&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OONI Probe CLI version:&lt;/strong&gt; 3.9.2&lt;/p&gt;











&lt;div&gt;
 &lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-probe-cli/images/image1.png"&gt;
 &lt;img
 src="https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-probe-cli/images/image1_hu_ad46b1e2bc630f.png"

 
 
 title="OONI Probe CLI"
 
 alt="OONI Probe CLI"
 
 /&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;OONI Probe is &lt;a href="https://github.com/ooni/probe"&gt;free and open source software&lt;/a&gt; that you can run to measure internet censorship and other forms of network interference.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This user guide provides step-by-step instructions on how to install and use the &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/install/cli"&gt;OONI Probe Command Line Interface (CLI)&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can run OONI Probe CLI on &lt;strong&gt;macOS&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Debian/Ubuntu Linux&lt;/strong&gt;, and on &lt;strong&gt;Raspberry Pis&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will get from this guide:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>User Guide: OONI Probe Desktop App</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-probe-desktop/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-probe-desktop/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Last updated:&lt;/strong&gt; 25th October 2022&lt;/p&gt;
