&lt;p&gt;OONI Probe is a &lt;a href="https://github.com/ooni/probe"&gt;free and open source&lt;/a&gt; app that you can use to measure internet censorship and other forms of network interference. This user guide provides &lt;strong&gt;step-by-step instructions&lt;/strong&gt; on how to install, run, and customize your use of the &lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/install/desktop/"&gt;OONI Probe desktop app&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>User Guide: OONI Probe Mobile App</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-probe-mobile/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-probe-mobile/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Last updated:&lt;/strong&gt; 15th April 2025&lt;/p&gt;
