&lt;p&gt;OONI Probe is a &lt;a href="https://github.com/ooni/probe"&gt;free and open source&lt;/a&gt; app that you can use to measure internet censorship and other forms of network interference. This user guide provides &lt;strong&gt;step-by-step instructions&lt;/strong&gt; on how to install, run, and customize your use of the &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/install/mobile"&gt;OONI Probe mobile app&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will get from this guide:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>User Guide: OONI Test Lists Editor</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/support/test-lists-editor/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/support/test-lists-editor/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Last updated:&lt;/strong&gt; 7th September 2022&lt;/p&gt;











&lt;div&gt;
 &lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/support/test-lists-editor/images/01.png"&gt;
 &lt;img
 src="https://ooni.github.io/support/test-lists-editor/images/01_hu_895f79e16af3285.png"

 
 
 title="Test Lists Editor"
 
 alt="Test Lists Editor"
 
 /&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href="https://test-lists.ooni.org/"&gt;OONI Test Lists Editor&lt;/a&gt; enables the public
to &lt;strong&gt;review and contribute to the lists of websites&lt;/strong&gt; (“&lt;a href="https://ooni.org/get-involved/contribute-test-lists"&gt;test lists&lt;/a&gt;”) that are &lt;strong&gt;tested for
censorship&lt;/strong&gt; by &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/install/"&gt;OONI Probe&lt;/a&gt; users around the
world.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This user guide provides &lt;strong&gt;step-by-step instructions&lt;/strong&gt; on how to use the
&lt;a href="https://test-lists.ooni.org/"&gt;Test Lists Editor&lt;/a&gt; to review and contribute
websites for censorship testing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Upon reading this guide, we hope you will feel empowered to contribute to test lists!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>